# {{brand_name}} Deck Creator

> Create branded presentation decks with consistent {{brand_name}} styling

## What This Skill Does

Generates PowerPoint (.pptx) presentations with {{brand_name}}'s brand styling pre-applied:
- Colors: {{primary_color}} (primary), {{secondary_color}} (secondary), {{accent_color}} (accents)
- Typography: {{font_heading}} (headings), {{font_body}} (body)
- Layouts: Title, content, closing slide templates

## Usage

```
User: "Create pitch deck for [topic]"

Skill:
1. Asks: How many slides? What sections?
2. Generates deck with branded templates
3. Populates with content (from user or draft copy)
4. Saves .pptx file

Output: presentation_[topic]_[date].pptx with {{brand_name}} styling
```

## Slide Templates

### Title Slide

**Layout**:
- Background: {{primary_color}}
- Title: {{font_heading}}, {{title_size}}, white
- Subtitle: {{font_body}}, {{subtitle_size}}, white/80% opacity
- Logo: Top-right or bottom-right (if available)

### Content Slide

**Layout**:
- Background: White
- Heading: {{font_heading}}, {{heading_size}}, {{primary_color}}
- Body: {{font_body}}, {{body_size}}, gray-800
- Bullets: {{accent_color}} bullet points
- Optional: Side accent bar ({{accent_color}}, left edge)

### Closing Slide

**Layout**:
- Background: {{secondary_color}}
- CTA: {{font_heading}}, large, white
- Contact info: {{font_body}}, white
- Logo: Centered or bottom

