## Customization

To modify slide templates:
1. Edit templates/slide-layouts.md
2. Regenerate deck (changes apply to new decks)

To change brand styling (colors, fonts):
- Do NOT edit this skill directly
- Re-run visual-identity meta-skill to regenerate with new styling
- This deck-creator skill will be regenerated with updated tokens
